import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap';

const Index = () => (
    // border bottom

      <Row>
        <Col>.col</Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>
  )
  export default Index
